      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must be under formal version control with regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; SQA plan must be documented and audited.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver has basic version control and a partial regression suite. No formal SQA plan audit has been completed. Achieved level 2 falls short of the required level 4 for MRL 5 Class III device context."
    },
    {
