      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions or equivalent must demonstrate order-of-accuracy convergence for the hemolysis transport equation and turbulence model employed.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy verification was performed for the Navier-Stokes solver but not for the power-law hemolysis transport equation. Achieved level 2 is insufficient for the required level 4."
    },
    {
