      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation-based GCI must be reported for hemolysis index on at least three systematically refined meshes; GCI must be below 5% on the fine mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study was completed; fine-mesh GCI is 8.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold. Achieved level 3 does not meet the required level 4."
    },
