      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be performed on the same pump geometry, fluid properties, and operating envelope as the COU; any deviation must be covered by a validated extrapolation argument.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic pump geometry at nominal conditions only; VAD-specific operating envelope deviations are not covered by an extrapolation argument. Achieved level 3 is insufficient for required level 5."
